{"tid":1050022,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以唔好乜柒都用「突發」？","createTime":"2019-03-06T16:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T18:14:45.000Z","uid":105795,"like":7,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4d44c968a440c2bae709247e08482822395e9fab","tid":1050022,"uid":105795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T16:49:02.000Z","msg":"突發，拼音是t&uacute; f&aacute;，是指出人意外地發生的事件。<br />\n<br />\n網路解釋：<br />\n1. sudden<br />\n2. burst forth<br />\n3. ejaculation<br />\n4. caprice<br />\n5. outbreak<br />\n<br />\n見到近期有個趨勢<br />\n啲人開post乜撚柒野都加突發兩個字上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nY3減價突發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n贏國Miniso又突發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連買部電話都要突發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底呢啲芝麻綠豆事有幾令人意外？<br />\n<br />\n靠加兩個字去引人睇post<br />\n同啲濕鳩content farm、標題黨有乜分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咪亂鳩用呢兩個字啦 真喺好撚un眼啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e5898a0a7617986dacb120064b136661f25828","tid":1050022,"uid":105795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T16:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DvRQQ0J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDvRQQ0J.jpg&h=be705a9d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nClickbait<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b61c7515a94cd41bd8aa87b3fb90085d3a194fa","tid":1050022,"uid":105795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T17:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VuDorA7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F